BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Blueprints and Breakthroughs - Brown County Schools - TEDx
DTSTART;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260516T083000
DTEND;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260516T143000
UID:260514rTkvrHLV1UO1H9pLGe0Bng
DESCRIPTION:Every bold idea starts with a blueprint—a vision sketched in
  the margins\, mapped on whiteboards\, or imagined in moments of quiet cur
 iosity. But blueprints alone don’t change the world. It takes courage\, 
 experimentation\, and perseverance to turn those plans into breakthroughs.
  At TEDxBrownCountySchools 2025\, we explore the intersection of design an
 d disruption\, planning and action\, imagination and impact. This year’s
  theme—Blueprints & Breakthroughs—celebrates the thinkers\, builders\,
  and changemakers who turn rough drafts into revolutions.\n\nWhether it’
 s a student reimagining education\, an innovator challenging rural norms\,
  or a quiet voice with a bold solution\, our stage will showcase the sketc
 hes that became sparks—and the sparks that became something bigger. Join
  us as we celebrate ideas worth building—and ideas worth breaking throug
 h.
LOCATION:Brown County Music
URL:https://www.eventbrite.com/e/tedx-brown-county-schools-blueprints-brea
 kthroughs-tickets-1982689322135
X-SOURCE:Limestone Post
END:VEVENT
