BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Linda Perry - Let It Die Here (2026)
DTSTART;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260605T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260605T210000
UID:260426g9KdO3azqkOJrWk7nQE2Pw
DESCRIPTION:*Let It Die Here* (2026)\n\n**Linda Perry** is one of the most
  outspoken and recognizable artists of the past 30 years. The hat\, tattoo
 s\, and massive hit single “What’s Up” with her band **4 Non-Blonde
 s** made her an icon.\n\nBut\, in the decades since that song topped the 
 charts\, Linda has reinvented herself as a Grammy-nominated songwriter and
  producer\, penning hit after hit for artists like Dolly Parton\, Christin
 a Aguilera\, Celine Dion\, Pink\, Adele\, Miley Cyrus\, Ariana Grande\, We
 ezer\, Gwen Stefani\, Alicia Keys\, The Chicks\, and others.\n\nWhile the 
 story of Linda’s career and craft is extraordinary\, this film is about 
 much more. *Let It Die Here* is an intimate look at a vulnerable and cou
 rageous woman as she navigates life-altering personal circumstances amidst
  gnawing career decisions. Linda’s past and present collide as she seeks
  to answer the big questions she can no longer avoid: Who am I? Am I loved
 ? What’s my purpose? What will I leave behind? The film features extraor
 dinary access to the artist\, including new footage\, performances\, and i
 nterviews with colleagues\, family\, and friends.\n\nRATED: N/A LENGTH: 1h
 r 40mins FORMAT: DCP
LOCATION:Buskirk Chumley Theater
URL:https://buskirkchumley.org/events/linda-perry-let-it-die-here-2026-jun
 e-5-2026/
X-SOURCE:Limestone Post
END:VEVENT
