BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:MoMoFo 100k and 20 mile Fun Run
DTSTART;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260605T083000
DTEND;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260605T083000
UID:260504tNV0OAp32EyaEobmX7Rojw
DESCRIPTION:This 100km trail race will prove that there’s more than just
  corn in Indiana! Situated in Indiana’s beautiful Morgan Monroe State Fo
 rest\, this evening-start event will have plenty to offer throughout the n
 ight with its old growth forests\, natural rock formations\, lakes\, and c
 reeks. Oh\, and did we mention the hills? With about 7\,500 feet of climbi
 ng—yes\, over 7k of climbing!—in addition to southern Indiana’s typi
 cal summertime heat and humidity\, this race is tougher than you’d think
 . Comprised of 85% single track\, 11% forest service road\, and 4% paved r
 oad \\(but with a generous cutoff time of 20 hours\\)\, we assure you that
  you won’t be disappointed. \n\nFor those less adventurous trail nuts we
  offer up our “fun run”. If you aren’t quite up for the full 100km w
 e have a 20 mile loop for you to “enjoy”. This run will start Saturday
  June 7 at 8:30am. You will have a SUPER generous 6 hours and 30 minutes t
 o complete one loop. This is the same loop as the 100k folks with the same
  unbelievable support at each aid station. \n\nWe invite you to experience
  true Hoosier hospitality with our fun and friendly trail running communit
 y.\n\nCome help make this a trail party…WooHoo!
LOCATION:Morgan Monroe State Forest
URL:https://indyrunners.org/view-race-details/momofo-100k-and-20-mile-fun-
 run/
X-SOURCE:Limestone Post
END:VEVENT
