BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tails on the Town
DTSTART;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260612T180000
DTEND;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260612T220000
UID:2603242i_23v5qFkejI_T_8K50yQ
DESCRIPTION:Tails on the Town\, presented by Scout's Honor\, is Monroe Cou
 nty Humane Association’s signature spring event. It is a carnival-themed
  evening for adults that brings together animal lovers to support pets in 
 our community. \n\nThe event includes carnival style games\, raffles\, gr
 eat food\, drinks\, live and silent auctions\, and music with DJShawnD. G
 uests enjoy a high energy atmosphere while connecting with others who care
  about pets and families in our community. All proceeds benefit programs a
 nd services at Monroe County Humane Association. \n\nTails on the Town is
  a 21 and older event. Come as you are in casual attire\, or dress up a
 nd join the fun. Either way\, you will fit right in.
LOCATION:The Woolery Mill
URL:https://www.monroehumane.org/tott
X-SOURCE:Limestone Post
END:VEVENT
