BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Jack Johnson SURFILMUSIC
DTSTART;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260626T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260626T190000
UID:260515CQ3XfGR0mU2GZXtVVHl45A
DESCRIPTION:***SURFILMUSIC* (2026)**\n\nA new documentary chronicling **
 Jack Johnson’s** evolution from surfer to filmmaker to world-renowned m
 usician.\n\nThe film traces how Jack’s early years making surf films wit
 h close friends became a foundation for a much broader creative life\, cap
 turing moments in and out of the water that later surfaced in his songwrit
 ing.\n\nBlending rare footage from those formative surf films and Jack’s
  personal and family archives with present-day reflections\, the film weav
 es together how lived experience\, friendship\, and exploration shaped the
  sound and stories behind the music.\n\nDirected by Emmett Malloy\, featur
 ing Jack Johnson\, Kelly Slater\, Rob Machado\, Gerry Lopez\, Chris Malloy
 \, G. Love\, Ben Harper\, John Florence\, Emmett Malloy\, Kim Johnson\, an
 d more\, with a beautiful score by Jack Johnson and Hermanos Gutiérrez. I
 n loving memory of Tamayo Perry.\n\nIn addition to the new film\, Jack has
  announced a companion double album\, *SURFILMUSIC Soundtrack* and 4-Tra
 cks\, arriving May 15 via Brushfire Records. The soundtrack features the f
 ilm’s original score by Jack Johnson and Hermanos Gutiérrez alongside r
 emastered selections from Jack’s early four-track recordings. 4-Tracks p
 resents a deeper dive into the archival music from Jack’s personal tapes
 \, including raw recordings and previously unreleased gems from his earlie
 st days making music.
LOCATION:Buskirk Chumley Theater
URL:https://buskirkchumley.org/events/jack-johnson-surfilmusic-2026-june-2
 6-2026/
X-SOURCE:Limestone Post
END:VEVENT
