BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Zach Rushing “Redneck Logic” Comedy Tour
DTSTART;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260709T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260709T214500
UID:251214D43TSF_9PEiiyGiG3_p92g
DESCRIPTION:I’m just a Mississippi boy with a loud mouth and a big heart
 . I grew up believing in hard work\, good friends\, and telling it like it
  is\, and I never really grew out of that. Most people know me from my com
 edy\, where I’ve built a career on being unapologetically myself. Whethe
 r I’m on stage for the Not-So-Rich-And-Famous Tour\, raising hell on soc
 ial media\, or telling stories that hit a little too close to home\, I try
  to keep it real and keep people laughing.\n\nBut I’m more than just a c
 omic. I run Triple B Outdoors\, where I get to share my love for hunting\,
  fishing\, and the outdoors with folks who live for the same things I do. 
 I’m engaged to the love of my life\, and when I’m not on the road\, yo
 u’ll find me in the woods\, on the water\, or working to grow my busines
 ses.\n\nAt the end of the day\, I’m not trying to be famous\, I’m just
  trying to be honest\, entertain people\, and maybe inspire a few along th
 e way. If you stick around\, you’ll get jokes\, a little wisdom\, and pr
 obably a few stories you wouldn’t want your grandma to hear.\n\nThis is 
 an 18+ event.
LOCATION:Buskirk Chumley Theater
URL:https://buskirkchumley.org/events/zach-rushing-redneck-logic-comedy-to
 ur-july-9-2026/
X-SOURCE:Limestone Post
END:VEVENT
