BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:PALS The Mane Event
DTSTART;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260724T173000
DTEND;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260724T173000
UID:260414tbTFiXBo60aoUat-s6ANww
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a remarkable evening at our **Mane Event Gala.**
  This event honors the incredible journey of our clients and the dedicate
 d community that makes it all possible. Together\, we'll celebrate **resi
 lience and recovery** following the rebuild of our entire campus followin
 g the May 16\, 2025 tornado. It truly is the "Year of the Horse" as we rel
 aunch as the **PALS Center for Wellness and Learning**.\n\nEnjoy an unfor
 gettable night featuring a **delicious dinner\, powerful client testimoni
 als\, a wine ring toss\, silent auction\, and a fun photo booth to captur
 e the memories**. \n\nDon’t miss this special evening!
LOCATION:The Woolery Mill
URL:https://palsindiana.org/
X-SOURCE:Limestone Post
END:VEVENT
