UID:250724ZiYnu6oDSkSZeFv0XzdxJQ
DESCRIPTION:Art Remains\, creative reuse center\, is having a garage sale 
 to clear out excess inventory and make room for new donations. Bring your 
 own shopping bags and shop the garage for fabric\, paints\, scrapbooking a
 nd collage materials\, picture frames and so much more. Pay what you can t
 o support the Art Remains mission of diverting craft materials from the la
 ndfill and making art affordable.
LOCATION:Art Remains Storage Garage
URL:http://Artremains.org
X-SOURCE:Limestone Post
END:VEVENT
